./domain (citybox)
	/boundcontextA (opendatahub)
		/domain-language-constructA.sh (upload_data.sh) (command)
		/domain-language-constructB.sh (create_torrent.sh) (command)
		/domain-language-constructC.sh (download_data.sh) (query)
	/boundedcontextB
		/domain-language-constructE.sh
		/domain-language-constructD.sh

Each Microservice have its own bounded-context with a portion of the domain-specific language.

Here we capture the domain verbs(commands and queries) into shellscripts. 

Each script takes arguments and creates nessesary events that gets stored into the ./DATA  
